Relay 2 (Light 2)	GPIO 3 (Pin 5)	VCC + GND
Relay 3 (Light 3)	GPIO 4 (Pin 7)	VCC + GND
Relay 4 (Light 4)	GPIO 17 (Pin 11)	VCC + GND
Relay 5 (Light 5)	GPIO 27 (Pin 13)	VCC + GND
Relay 6 (Light 6)	GPIO 22 (Pin 15)	VCC + GND
Relay 7 (Light 7)	GPIO 10 (Pin 19)	VCC + GND
Relay 8 (Light 8)	GPIO 9 (Pin 21)	VCC + GND
